    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-03-14T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-03-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="498"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d498">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 14, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Porte by note reassures me that full instructions have been sent by telegram
                    to secure public tranquillity. It declares that apprehensions in the interior
                    have been caused by revolutionists and have no foundation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
